manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: The Easiest Way to Organize Your Stuff Keep your car free from clutter with our versatile car seat organizer and storage! Made from premium materials, its durable construction is built to last. It's designed with multiple pockets and a removable pouch, so you can detach it and bring your valuables outside. The included LCD tablet features easy-to-use fasteners for quick and hassle-free attachment to the organizer.

A Handy Helper of Moms Taking a stroll with your little loved ones? Our back of seat organizer for car doubles as a stroller organizer, so you can bring all your child's essentials! It securely attaches to a stroller handle, so you won't need to bring a diaper bag. Simply move the organizer from your car to your baby's stroller and you can head out in no time!

Practical & Space-Saving Design Enjoy Clutter-Free & Fuss-Free Car Trips! Traveling with your little ones? Make sure you bring all their stuff (and snacks), so they can enjoy the ride! Our car back seat organizer for kids keeps all your child's essentials organized, so they can quickly reach what they need. Designed to offer plenty of storage space, you can store your valuables, along with your kids belongings, in our handy car seat organizer!

reviews.reviewText: Really like these. Should've measured my seat though and paid a little more attention to dimensions because they are just slightly skinnier than I'd like, but they still work absolutely perfectly for what I was wanting. Install was fairly simple and easy. They seem like they're very nice quality and I'm very pleased.*Edit: still leaving original comments but wanted to add a couple of things after using for a bit. The party about me not measuring or paying attention to how wide they are has bit me I little more in the butt than what I expected as it was too keep a toddlers feet off the back of my seat and now sed toddler puts their feet beside the edges of the organizer so still on my seats. That's my fault not sellers just hoping that this helps others to measure before they buy. However, there is a manufacturer issue with the wipe holder. I'm not sure exactly what type of wipes are expected to go in the holder but I have parent choice and you have to squeeze really hard to get the package to fit in and the opening for the package does not work with the opening for holder like at all.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 13, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Easy to Install / Protects Seats / Storage
reviews.reviewText: Love these! They were easy to install. However, I did wrap the lower strap through the seat cover at the bottom and it holds very well; without having a cord/strap wrap around the front of the seats.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 7, 2018
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Didn't work for me
reviews.reviewText: The tablet pocket is a nice size for a variety of tablets the zipper for the headphone or charger port is convenient seeing that all tablets are made equally. I wasn't a fan of how much space that wasn't being used when not in use. The headphone holder is detachable which made it easy to possibly lose. So I kept it in the "pocket for valuable" which is a small zipper pocket attached to the organizer located in the same area of the Velcro for the wipes holder. I found this location to be difficult to put items in for bulking up the Velcro making it harder to keep the wipes holder on the designated area. I was impressed by the wipes holder ability to contain a full pack of wipes (about 70 ct) and keep them moist, even though I had a hard time keeping it attached to the organizer. In the minivan it would get knocked off by passengers trying to get in the rear seat. Although the cupholders are generous the strechy mesh pockets are not. I didn't get to use for a stroller. But the straps for this feature doesn't tend to stick out the side which is pro or con depending on your needs.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on March 14, 2019
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars light weight and easy to install/take out
reviews.reviewText: works great for my kids tablets when we are traveling so they can watch a movie and not drop the tablet, or when they don't need the tablet it stores it safely so it doesn't end up on the floor. Wipe container allows them to clean up spills on their own or I have tissues in one side so they can use that when needed. The extra pocket works great for storing coloring books, and other kids toys and the bottle holder works good for their travel water bottles or other snacks. easy to take out and put on a stroller or kids wagon to use in a different setting as well.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 28, 2018
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars It’s made well the straps are easy to attach and don’t come loose
reviews.reviewText: It’s made well the straps are easy to attach and don’t come loose, and the entire thing attaches easily to the stroller and the backseat of my SUV. Would work well in any car. Very cool.
